title: PAF kills terrorists, pounds hideouts in Khyber Agency: ISPR
text:
0 0 
RAWALPINDI: The Pakistan Air Force carried out an operation in Rajagal Area of Khyber Agency on Tuesday where several terrorists were killed, the military wing Inter-service Public Relations said. 
Several militant hideouts were destroyed in the area which borders Afghanistan. 
After a week of deadly militant attacks and bombings killed at least 100 people in Pakistan, security forces have initiated a countrywide crackdown, nabbing suspects and carrying out search operations.
